                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17770409-47-defend436 t17770409-47-punish239"></join>
               Death
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the Second Middlesex Jury before Mr. 
               <persName id="t17770409-47-person451">
                  Baron
                   EYRE
               <interp inst="t17770409-47-person451" type="surname" value="EYRE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770409-47-person451" type="given" value="Baron"></interp>
